        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/maani-al-akhbar:147:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/28/1/147/1",
        "text": [
          ": السامة القرابة، والهامة هو أم الأرض  ، واللامة لمم الشياطين، والعامة عامة الناس."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.basel-kadem": [
            "1.\tMy father, may Allah grant him mercy, (narrated) from Muhammed bin Yahya, from Ahmad bin Muhammed bin Musa bin Ja’far, from more than one of our companions, from Sulayman bin Khalid, from Abu Abdillah, peace be upon him, that he was asked about the saying of Allah’s Messenger, Allah’s blessings be upon him and his Family: «I seek refuge in You from the evil of saama, haama, ‘aamma and laama». So he said: Saama is kinship, haama is the mother of earth, laama is the minor sins of demons and ‘aamma is the general people."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
